<A>__{captain amazing abandons his jet pack and moves across the old slate roof like spiderman, leaping nimbly from gable to gable and walking along a high ridge like a tight rope walker. finally he approaches a skylight, looks down and sees... a huge old library with an iron catwalk running around it. casanova frankenstein sits in a club chair by a roaring tire. anabel perches on the arm of his chair. in the other chair sits a once good looking, now paunchy guy, with a meticulously coiffed haircut. he is tony pompadour, head of the infamous disco boys.}
